[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "と、いうことで……お連れしました！\nシャッフェン科学学校のハイディさんです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00530",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "どもー。話は聞いてるよ、お三方。\nこの私の力を頼りたいってね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00531",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なんだか、随分軽いのが来たわね。\n本当に頼れるわけ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00532",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "おっ、言うねー？　確かに専門分野じゃないけどさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00533",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "でも、頼まれたからにはやるよ。\nこの前のライブも楽しませてもらったし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00534",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "見ててくれたんだ！　あのライブ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00535",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "見ていたとも！\n……演出に錬金術が使われてたところもね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00536",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "あんなことされて、科学者が黙ってられるかっての！\n見てなさいレスナ！　そっちよりすごいことしてやる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00537",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "ええっ、私！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00538",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なんか、雰囲気変わったわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00539",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ハイディ殿に何があったのでありましょうな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00540",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "とにかく！　やるからには本気でサポートするよ。\nそちらの社長さんにも話は付けてきたから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00541",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "え、社長殿に？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00542",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "本当のことですわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00543",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "シャッフェン科学学校の教諭にも交渉し、フェスまでの\n期間限定で技術スタッフとして雇いましたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00544",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "相変わらず、その辺り手が早いわね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00545",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "カメラや編集用のＰＣも貸し出してくださるとのこと。\n大事に使うんですのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00546",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "助かりまする！\nこれを機に拙者も編集の勉強をしたいでござるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00547",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "それで？　ＳＮＳバズを狙った動画を作るんだっけ。\nやることは決まったの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00548",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "色々と考えてはみたんだけど、\n一番最初はやっぱり自己紹介動画かなって思うんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00549",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "ま、妥当なところか。\n始めるってなったら声かけて！　準備しておくから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00550",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "了解！　ではヨハナにイザナ、\n台本をまとめるでござるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00551",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "それにしても、バズかあ。\nなんだかここでのグループ実習を思い出すよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00552",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "ビジネススクールの二人の手も\n借りられたらよかったんだけどなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00553",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "プラフタさんとクラウディアさんは、今別の案件で\n忙しいそうで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00554",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "はいはい、どうせハイディちゃんは暇な冬休みを\n過ごしてますよーだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00555",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "シャッフェン科学学校の２年生。\n科学技術を学んでおり、錬金術をライバル視している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]